Mercer is a global consulting leader in advancing health, wealth, and career for its clients. As part of the Marsh McLennan family, Mercer specializes in providing strategic advice and solutions in the areas of employee benefits, talent management, retirement planning, and investment consulting. The company supports businesses in optimizing their workforce strategies, enhancing organizational performance, and ensuring financial security for employees. With a presence in over 40 countries and a network of experts worldwide, Mercer combines data-driven insights with innovative approaches to address complex organizational challenges.
